Class FillManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mapbox.mapboxsdk.plugins.annotation.AnnotationManager<FillLayer,Fill,FillOptions,OnFillDragListener,OnFillClickListener,OnFillLongClickListener>
      • com.mapbox.mapboxsdk.plugins.annotation.FillManager

  • public class FillManager
extends AnnotationManager<FillLayer,Fill,FillOptions,OnFillDragListener,OnFillClickListener,OnFillLongClickListener>
    The fill manager allows to add fills to a map.

      • create

        public List<Fill> create(String json)
        Create a list of fills on the map.

        Fills are going to be created only for features with a matching geometry.

        You can inspect a full list of supported feature properties in FillOptions.fromFeature(Feature).

        Parameters:
        json - the GeoJSON defining the list of fills to build
        Returns:
        the list of built fills
